Jack & June Murray
Four Lakes will be our only retirement community! When we first visited Four Lakes, we were surprised at all the activities available including the restaurant, great parties and entertainment. The olympic size swimming pool is terrific after playing golf on Four Lakes challenging 18 hole golf course. Four Lakes is near all the Theme parks which is just the excuse for our grandkids to visit. Well we got to go now we are off to the casino, one of Four Lakes many day trips. We can honestly say that moving to Four Lakes was the best decision we ever made!
Sign Up For Our Newsletter
We strive to provide the very best in Florida retirement, and we do that by keeping you in the know. Sign up below to be added to our Email newsletter! Receive updates on our current promotions, reduced price homes, and upcoming events!
